caption.p: Genetic characterization of Korle-bu Aedes virus (KoBV). ( A) KoBV genome showing the predicted stop codon read through. ( B) Evolutionary history of KoBV. Maximum likelihood tree constructed with the conserved amino acid domain of the genome sequence with Genbank accession number LC496785. The conserved domains were extracted using MAFFT 7 online version [ 27] and the Gblocks program [ 28]. Bootstrap support values from 1000 bootstrap replicates are indicated on the branches.
